{"title":"一天，这样开始","authors":["葛崇岳"],"dates":[{"year":1991,"month":2,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"一天，这样开始"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"葛崇岳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一本书打开了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"很浓的墨香味儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"许多健美的词组精力充沛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生命在字里行间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活泼如美丽的飞鸟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清新与流畅的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红绿灯惬意地眨着眼睛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而我们迎候太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎候每天最有力的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巨轮的搏动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"城市"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举着高大建筑物"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举着市花市树"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笼罩着如诗如雾般的想象"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"街心公园立交桥喷水池"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和栩栩如生的俊美群雕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被露珠染上晶莹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"染上我们独特与透明的宁静"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倒影在静静沉思中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呈现青铜色彩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而火焰的小漩涡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铜纽扣一样在胸襟上闪耀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车流量陡涨的长街"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从东到西河一样滔滔不绝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"力量与智慧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳动与创造"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在共和国的肌体里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如血液欢畅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们追逐和等候什么"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们仰望太阳并祝福什么"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们　人们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在宁静与净洁的繁华中 　 同样耀升如灿灿之日啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每天　从这个时刻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那本书打开了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新的一页"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们寻找最新的语汇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"组成共和国和我们城市"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"完全崭新的一天！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}